siteMeta.description: I am the man with no name, Zapp Brannigan! It’s a T. Please, Don-Bot… look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file!.

page.title: Editors
page.excerpt: Bite my shiny metal ass. The key to victory is discipline, and that means a well made bed. You will practice until you can make your bed in your sleep. A sexy mistake. Goodbye, friends. I never thought I’d die like this. But I always really hoped. No. We’re on the top. With a warning…

pages.title: Philip J. Fry
pages.content:
We’re rescuing ya. Who said that? SURE you can die! You want to die?! Pansy. I didn’t ask for a completely reasonable excuse! I asked you to get busy! Meh.

Too much work. Let’s burn it and say we dumped it in the sewer. Incidentally, you have a dime up your nose. Doomsday device? Ah, now the ball’s in Farnsworth’s court! I’ve been there. My folks were always on me to groom myself and wear underpants. What am I, the pope?

Why am I sticky and naked? Did I miss something fun? No, of course not. It was… uh… porno. Yeah, that’s it. Who are those horrible orange men? Fry! Quit doing the right thing, you jerk! I decline the title of Iron Cook and accept the lesser title of Zinc Saucier, which I just made up. Uhh… also, comes with double prize money.

We’ll need to have a look inside you with this camera. Dear God, they’ll be killed on our doorstep! And there’s no trash pickup until January 3rd. But, like most politicians, he promised more than he could deliver.
pages.excerpt: Yes, I saw. You were doing well, until everyone died. Hey, whatcha watching? You lived before you met me?! Please, Don-Bot… look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file! Throw her in the brig.

pages.title: Turanga Leela
pages.content:
Yep, I remember. They came in last at the Olympics, then retired to promote alcoholic beverages! I wish! It’s a nickel. I usually try to keep my sadness pent up inside where it can fester quietly as a mental illness.

Why did you bring us here? Okay, I like a challenge. I am the man with no name, Zapp Brannigan! I am the man with no name, Zapp Brannigan! It’s a T. It goes “tuh”.

Actually, that’s still true. Is that a cooking show? Hi, I’m a naughty nurse, and I really need someone to talk to. $9.95 a minute. Daddy Bender, we’re hungry.

And why did ‘I’ have to take a cab? I’m a thing. Take me to your leader! I’ve been there. My folks were always on me to groom myself and wear underpants. What am I, the pope? Fry! Stay back! He’s too powerful!
pages.excerpt: Please, Don-Bot… look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file! That could be ‘my’ beautiful soul sitting naked on a couch. If I could just learn to play this stupid thing. Man, I’m sore all over. I feel like I just went ten rounds with mighty Thor.

childPages.title: Bender Bending Rodriguez
childPages.excerpt: For one beautiful night I knew what it was like to be a grandmother. Subjugated, yet honored. I barely knew Philip, but as a clergyman I have no problem telling his most intimate friends all about him.
